	// format, "$PROVIDER/$MODEL_NAME". A single-item slice with value '*' means
	// that all models in the 'master allowlist' are allowed.
	//
	// DO NOT USE DIRECTLY when enforcing permissions: use EvaluateAllowedModels(...)
